title: E96 Watergate

description:
In this episode, the team discusses the Watergate scandal with distinguished journalist, best-selling historian, and author of the new book, "Watergate: A New History", Garrett M. Graff.

Go to GarrettGraff.com to find links to his books, podcast episodes, and much more!
